---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - ELVIRA" 
  description="Review the terms and conditions governing the use of ELVIRA's digital concierge platform for hotels."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 border-b pb-4" data-i18n="terms.title">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600" data-i18n="terms.lastUpdated">Last Updated: June 1, 2025</p>
      
      <div class="mt-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="p-8 prose prose-blue max-w-none text-justify">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.agreement">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p data-i18n="terms.agreement.p1">
            By accessing or using ELVIRA's digital concierge platform, website, and services (collectively, the "Services"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our Services.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="terms.agreement.p2">
            These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you and ELVIRA ("we," "our," or "us") regarding your use of our Services.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.description">2. Service Description</h2>
          <p data-i18n="terms.description.p1">
            ELVIRA provides a digital concierge platform designed for hotels to enhance guest experiences. Our platform allows hotels to offer digital services to their guests, including room service ordering, activity bookings, hotel information, and live chat with hotel staff.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="terms.description.p2">
            The Services are available to two types of users:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li data-i18n="terms.description.users.hotels"><strong>Hotel Partners:</strong> Hotels that subscribe to our platform to offer digital concierge services to their guests.</li>
            <li data-i18n="terms.description.users.guests"><strong>End Users (Guests):</strong> Hotel guests who access the platform during their stay.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.account">3. Account Registration and Security</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.account.hotelPartners">3.1 Hotel Partner Accounts</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.account.hotelPartners.p1">
            To use our Services as a Hotel Partner, you must create an account. You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information during the registration process and to update such information to keep it accurate, current, and complete.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="terms.account.hotelPartners.p2">
            You are responsible for safeguarding your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.account.guestAccess">3.2 Guest Access</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.account.guestAccess.p1">
            Hotel guests access the platform using a temporary verification code provided by the hotel. This code is linked to their room and expires after checkout. Guests are responsible for keeping their verification code secure during their stay.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.subscription">4. Subscription and Payment Terms</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.subscription.plans">4.1 Subscription Plans</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.subscription.plans.p1">
            Hotel Partners can choose from various subscription plans based on hotel size and feature requirements. Pricing information is available on our website or through direct consultation with our sales team.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.subscription.payment">4.2 Payment</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.subscription.payment.p1">
            Hotel Partners agree to pay all fees associated with their chosen subscription plan. Payments are due in advance, either monthly or annually, depending on the selected billing cycle.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="terms.subscription.payment.p2">
            We use trusted third-party payment processors. By providing payment information, you authorize us to charge your designated payment method for all fees incurred.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.subscription.taxes">4.3 Taxes</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.subscription.taxes.p1">
            All fees are exclusive of applicable taxes. Hotel Partners are responsible for paying all taxes associated with their use of our Services.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.subscription.refunds">4.4 Refunds</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.subscription.refunds.p1">
            Our refund policy is outlined in your subscription agreement. Generally, subscription fees are non-refundable except as required by law or as specifically provided in these Terms.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.termination">5. Term and Termination</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.termination.term">5.1 Term</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.termination.term.p1">
            These Terms will remain in effect until terminated by either you or us.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.termination.byHotels">5.2 Termination by Hotel Partners</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.termination.byHotels.p1">
            Hotel Partners may terminate their subscription at any time by providing written notice. Termination will be effective at the end of the current billing cycle.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.termination.byELVIRA">5.3 Termination by ELVIRA</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.termination.byELVIRA.p1">
            We may terminate or suspend your access to the Services immediately, without prior notice or liability, for any reason, including if you breach these Terms.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.termination.effect">5.4 Effect of Termination</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.termination.effect.p1">
            Upon termination, your right to use the Services will immediately cease. All provisions of the Terms that should survive termination shall survive, including ownership provisions, warranty disclaimers, indemnity, and limitations of liability.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.responsibilities">6. User Responsibilities and Prohibited Activities</h2>
          <p data-i18n="terms.responsibilities.intro">
            When using our Services, you agree not to:
