          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.ip.license">7.2 License to Use</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.ip.license.p1">
            We grant Hotel Partners a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use our Services as outlined in their subscription plan. Hotel guests receive a limited license to use the platform during their stay.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.ip.feedback">7.3 Feedback</h3>
          <p data-i18n="terms.ip.feedback.p1">
            If you provide us with feedback or suggestions regarding our Services, you grant us the right to use this feedback without restriction or compensation.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900" data-i18n="terms.sections.thirdParty">8. Third-Party Services and Content</h2>
